data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch-style home! Nestled in the serene Horse Creek neighborhood, this property boasts a fully finished walkout basement that doubles your living space. Step inside to discover updated exterior doors by Anderson welcoming you into a bright and airy interior. The newer stainless steel appliances and plantation shutters add to a laundry list of upgrades. This impeccably cared-for home features not just one, but two convenient laundry areas, ensuring laundry day is a breeze. With newer vinyl flooring throughout, including stylish and durable options, this residence effortlessly combines modern aesthetics with practicality. Enjoy the charm of brand new carpeting in the basement, adding warmth and comfort to the space. Embrace eco-friendly living with a fully paid off solar system, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings. Relish in the beauty of sunrise views from your new deck, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. Conveniently located just minutes from Main Street in Parker, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Experience the epitome of entertainment with your very own movie theater, complete with all furniture included for cozy movie nights with family and friends. Need a space for projects? Look no further than the basement's workbench, ideal for DIY enthusiasts or hobbyists. With a neighborhood park just a stone's throw away, outdoor recreation is right at your fingertips. This home offers the perfect blend of modern updates, convenience, and leisure, making it an ideal retreat for anyone seeking comfort and relaxation in Parker's vibrant community.
